name: DESMODUS
description:
I'd like to introduce two significant characters in this first serial killer.

Demodus (left) is a mortal with a vampire-bat obsession. She satisfies her craving by feasting on human blood.
Headroach (right) is Demodus’s pet. A scientist's experiment fused from a dying human head and cockroach legs. Headroach has no desire to eat or drink.
